			<xsd:documentation>A data type of Code SHOULD identify a data point that is a look-up value for an entry in a list of values and explanations and MAY have CodeOwnerURI and CodeEffectiveDate attributes.
EXAMPLE: A State Code would be expressed as "AL".</xsd:documentation>
