			<xsd:documentation>A data type of String SHOULD identify a data point that is either a text value consisting of a word, phrase, sentence, paragraph, or formatted (TAB, CR, LF) character content depending on its purpose or a numeric value with a maximum of 16383 characters and MAY have the lang attribute. There is no list of valid values provided.
